data.title: Dell Technologies, Inc. Company Profile: Financials, Valuation, and Growth
data.meta_description: Dell is a privately-held, private equity-backed information technology and electronics company that offers a broad range of products and services. Dell's services include sales of personal computers and workstations, personal electronics, software and hosted services. Dell was incorporated in 1984 and was founded by Michael Dell. The company is headquartered in Round Rock, Texas.
